==English==
===Noun===
'''proboscis''' (''plural'' '''proboscises''' or '''proboscides''')

# {{anatomy}} An elongated tube from the head or connected to the mouth, of an animal. 
## The tubular feeding and sucking organ of certain [[invertebrate]]s like [[insect]]s, [[worm]]s and [[mollusc]]s.
## The trunk of an [[elephant]].
# Informally, a large human nose.


====Derived terms====
* [[proboscis monkey]].
